content_sections.title: Details
content_sections.content:
You can test your TypeScript skills with ' Quiz.
The Test
The test contains 25 questions and there is no time limit.
The test is not official, it's just a nice way to see how much you know, or don't know, about TypeScript.
Count Your Score
You will get 1 point for
each correct answer. At the end of the Quiz, your total score will be displayed.
Maximum score is 25 points.
Start the Quiz
Good luck!
Start the TypeScript Quiz ❯
If you don't know TypeScript, we suggest that you read our
TypeScript Tutorial
from scratch.
